    <body>
        <p>You can return the workspace to the saved configuration of the layout. In other words, if you are working in a particular layout and have opened different interface elements or moved interface elements around, you can select this option to go back to the saved configuration.</p>
        <p>Select  <span class="Emphasis">Window &gt; Reload Layout</span>.</p>
    </body>
</html>